OL,7,FThe leader of a sex cult in Kidwelly
OL,8,Fwho preyed on children could be moved
OL,9,Fto an open prison, following
OL,10,Frecommendations by the Parole Board.
OL,12,FIn 2011, Colin Batley was convicted of
OL,13,F35 charges after he operated as the
OL,14,Fself-styled high priest of a cult,
OL,15,Fwhich he ran from homes in a quiet cul-
OL,16,Fde-sac.
OL,18,FHe was jailed for a minimum of 11
OL,19,Fyears and warned he could be behind
OL,20,Fbars for life.
