OL,7,FThe Parole Board noted at the time he
OL,8,Fhad an obsession with sex and "child
OL,9,Fabuse supportive beliefs" and showed a
OL,10,F"callous disregard" for the feelings
OL,11,Fof victims.
OL,13,FHowever, in a recent review of his
OL,14,Feligibility for parole, the panel
OL,15,Fheard of Batley's work to address his
OL,16,Fsexual offending and that his
OL,17,Fbehaviour in prison was "exemplary".
