OL,7,FWhile Batley agreed his release "would
OL,8,Fnot be a good idea" at this stage, he
OL,9,Fsaid he wanted to build on his skills
OL,10,Fin an open prison.
OL,12,FOpen prisons have minimal security and
OL,13,Fallow eligible prisoners to spend most
OL,14,Fof their day out of prison on licence,
OL,15,Ffor example, to carry out work or
OL,16,Feducation.
OL,18,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood will
OL,19,Fmake the final decision on whether to
OL,20,Faccept the panel's recommendations.
